{"tid":2081123,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛係一種能力","createTime":"2020-06-27T03:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T14:47:35.000Z","uid":186374,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c0a569bf9ebe8442e38351bdb55720b20eb9a0","tid":2081123,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"唔愛/唔夠愛/淡咗乜乜柒柒<br />\n都係藉口<br />\n玩具你可以玩厭<br />\n愛唔係會厭嘅野 往壞發展會成恨 往好發展會升華成親<br />\n<br />\n根本絕大部分人都係唔識愛 偏要繼續玩談戀愛嘅遊戲<br />\n輸完又輸燈蛾撲火 然後怪自己遇人不淑<br />\n或者拈花惹草閱人無數 然後沾沾自喜<br />\n<br />\n記得有條好經典嘅youtube片講過<br />\n有啲人好中意食魚 會話 i love fish<br />\nyou don't love fish<br />\nyou just like the taste of it<br />\n<br />\n如果想去學習 已經係邁出咗第一步<br />\n祝大家遇到嘅另一半都係肯去學習愛嘅人"},{"pid":"970f6c5f0db0d94d8db67cedef933a6d190f6a8a","tid":2081123,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DuJsYy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDuJsYy0.jpg&h=8b28e3b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"895051af1ee57aabfc19689f173f0328278f15c4","tid":2081123,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"dsldnsn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}